1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:17,039 --> 00:00:19,260
The two of you are high-ranking
Gate Bureau constables.

4
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:23,280
Yet, you quarreled like street thugs
in front of your subordinates.

5
00:00:23,962 --> 00:00:25,043
Unacceptable.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:27,879
My apologies, sir.

7
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,399
Grandpa,

8
00:00:29,679 --> 00:00:31,440
Mao Buyu is clearly losing his judgment.

9
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,799
He's protecting the Jade Squirrel.

10
00:00:32,799 --> 00:00:33,439
Wushuang!

11
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:35,479
Until there's a conviction,
you can't accuse Chang.

12
00:00:35,479 --> 00:00:35,840
I...

13
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:36,479
Enough.

14
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:39,100
Maintain your composure
during a major case.

15
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:40,479
I've filed the report.

16
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:41,600
In three days,

17
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:44,119
the Vice Minister himself
will interrogate Lin Xin'er.

18
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:47,479
The truth will come to light then.

19
00:00:47,479 --> 00:00:48,799
The Vice Minister is taking over

20
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:50,520
just to get Lin Xin'er's testimony?

21
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,119
This...

22
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:53,280
Isn't that a bit excessive?

23
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:56,000
Grandpa is doing this
to close the case as soon as possible.

24
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:57,560
As long as the case remains open,

25
00:00:58,039 --> 00:01:00,520
Ms. Chu has to stay behind bars.

26
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:01,600
In that case,

27
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,320
if there is no concrete evidence

28
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,920
proving Chang is the Jade Squirrel,

29
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:07,079
she should be released immediately.

30
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,840
And if the evidence is solid,

31
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,079
she should be beheaded in public.

32
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,280
Shuang!

33
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:15,920
Even if Lin Xin'er's word is suspect,

34
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,719
Chu Yunchang is still
the primary suspect.

35
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,599
Out of everyone she could have named,

36
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,920
why did she pick Chu Yunchang

37
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,920
as the Jade Squirrel?

38
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,599
A random accusation
or a personal grudge.

39
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,439
Either is possible.

40
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,439
You...

41
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,760
You just want to clear your lover's name.

42
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,640
Chang is innocent.

43
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,640
It's only right to prove her innocence.

44
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:32,760
But...

45
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:35,760
Buyu.

46
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:38,719
What matters right now
is finding the evidence.

47
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:42,280
The Gate Bureau will never
frame an innocent soul,

48
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,280
but we won't let
a criminal walk free either.

49
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:47,560
- Understood, Commissioner.
- Understood, Commissioner.

50
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,439
Buyu.

51
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:58,040
You're my right-hand man.

52
00:01:58,060 --> 00:02:00,040
The most capable always
end up with the most work.

53
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,319
There's one more matter
I need you to handle.

54
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:04,280
Name it, Commissioner.

55
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,840
I'll give it my full attention.

56
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:07,480
Grandpa!

57
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,000
You have to help me!

58
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,879
One of your constables here
is a real piece of work.

59
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,560
He bullied me the moment I arrived!

60
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,479
He even threw me in a cell!

61
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,439
You have to make him pay!

62
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,439
It was him!

63
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,439
Right there!

64
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,800
That's the guy, Grandpa!

65
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,990
Wuxia, enough of your nonsense.

66
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:26,960
Buyu is the finest in our ranks.

67
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:28,080
Listen closely.

68
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,960
From now on, he is your master.

69
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:30,800
Me?

70
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,439
That's what I wanted
to discuss with you.

71
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,240
Buyu,

72
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:34,919
take Wuxia under your wing.

73
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,240
Train him hard and well.

74
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,919
Grandpa, no! Wait!

75
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,319
Fine by me,

76
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,360
dear disciple.

77
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,680
Stay away! Get away from me!

78
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,120
No!

79
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,840
Stop it!

80
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,290
It wasn't me! I didn't do it!

81
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:55,400
It wasn't me!

82
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,680
Please, just leave me alone!

83
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:04,199
You...

84
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,080
Stay away from me!

85
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,080
I'm begging you.

86
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,800
Please.

87
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,840
Just let me sleep, okay?

88
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,199
I'm begging you!

89
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,510
The Ministry of Justice is coming
to interrogate you tomorrow.

90
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,639
Our time is running out.

91
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,039
So, listen up.

92
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,680
You have two choices here.

93
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,319
One, you cooperate with me.

94
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,159
Or two,

95
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,159
a nightmare worse than death.

96
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,639
Fine.

97
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:36,319
Ask whatever you want.

98
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,319
But once you're done,

99
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,919
you have to let me get some sleep.

100
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,879
Deal.

101
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,800
First question.

102
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,919
Have you ever seen the Sacred Token?

103
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,000
The Sacred Token?

104
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,639
The Sacred Token...

105
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,080
The Sacred Token...

106
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,159
I remember seeing it

107
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,000
with my master when I was a kid.

108
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,800
But I haven't seen it since.

109
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:02,080
The one I had was a replica

110
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:05,680
made by Jia Yizhen based on my memory.

111
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,240
Who is your master?

112
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,800
Master?

113
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,439
My master...

114
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,520
My master...

115
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,160
No, no!

116
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,040
I can't say!

117
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,240
I can't say anything!

118
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,519
I'm begging you...

119
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,040
I'm begging you, just let me go!

120
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,600
Please, just let me go!

121
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,199
Please!

122
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:26,839
How can your mental state be this weak?

123
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,839
You're far too fragile.

124
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,720
The alarm!

125
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:36,079
What are you all standing around for?

126
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,279
Catch the thief!

127
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,279
Guards! Someone!

128
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,160
My silver! It's all gone!

129
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,319
The Jade Squirrel struck again!

130
00:04:53,012 --> 00:04:54,012
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)

131
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,680
Grandpa,

132
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,759
this has to be the work
of an accomplice.

133
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,920
Trust me on this.

134
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,199
Chu Yunchang is locked in a cell,

135
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:03,839
yet the Jade Squirrel is still
roaming free in the Capital.

136
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,759
Now that Lin Xin'er is incoherent,

137
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,079
the Vice Minister will see this

138
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,240
during the interrogation

139
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:11,199
and inevitably release Chu Yunchang.

140
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:13,079
This is clearly that woman's scheme.

141
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:15,399
The whole city is in a state of panic,

142
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,879
yet you're still fixated on

143
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,360
the woman behind bars.

144
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:20,600
How am I supposed to
explain this to my superiors?

145
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:21,439
Grandpa.

146
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,600
Please, give me one more chance.

147
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,680
Chu Yunchang.

148
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,199
You are the Jade Squirrel, aren't you?

149
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,480
Where is your proof?

150
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,240
Lin Xin'er identified you herself.

151
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:38,199
Fine.

152
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,519
If you can get her
to identify me one more time,

153
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,800
I'll confess.

154
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,519
Driving her mad

155
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,560
won't get you off the hook.

156
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,040
Today,

157
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,560
I'm getting a confession.

158
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:54,439
Are you going
to beat a confession out of me?

159
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,660
Whether you're innocent or not,
we'll find out after the beating.

160
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,480
Luo Wushuang,

161
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,040
do you know the consequences

162
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,720
of illegal torture?

163
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,639
And how will you look

164
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,120
after I'm done with you?

165
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:10,639
Do it!

166
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,480
Stop!

167
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,000
Don't you dare.

168
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,120
Not on my watch.

169
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,839
Buyu, don't get in my way.

170
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,839
Wushuang, do you realize
what you're doing?

171
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:29,040
You'll be stripped
of your rank for this!

172
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,279
If I deliver results,

173
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,480
nobody cares about the process.

174
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,120
Do it!

175
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,160
Mao Buyu!

176
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,319
Nobody moves!

177
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,639
Mao Buyu...

178
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,600
You're really doing this for her?

179
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:46,199
Wushuang, I'm saving you
from a mistake you can't fix.

180
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,439
If you actually cared about me,

181
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:49,800
you wouldn't be stopping me.

182
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,079
Do it!

183
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,279
Buyu!

184
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,360
- Yu!
- Buyu!

185
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,319
Buyu!

186
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,720
How could you be so reckless, Yu?

187
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,279
Reporting!

188
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:18,120
Constables.

189
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,480
What is it?

190
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,590
Vice Minister Zhou is here.

191
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:32,425
(Ministry of Justice)

192
00:07:32,575 --> 00:07:34,600
(Vice Minister of Justice)

193
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:50,639
Bring in the prisoner Lin Xin'er
and the suspect Chu Yunchang.

194
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,600
Lin Xin'er.

195
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,639
You've been convicted of your crimes.

196
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,240
We won't discuss them further today.

197
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,879
You identified Chu Yunchang

198
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:17,240
as the Jade Squirrel, Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect.

199
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,240
Do you have any proof?

200
00:08:48,675 --> 00:08:49,625
(Upholding the Law)

201
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:06,960
Vice Minister.

202
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,679
The prisoner killed herself.

203
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:15,240
How do you run this place?

204
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:19,159
You brought a lunatic
for me to interrogate?

205
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,360
Get her out of here.

206
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,159
Yes, sir.

207
00:09:26,175 --> 00:09:27,950
(Upholding the Law)

208
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,360
Enough.

209
00:09:31,090 --> 00:09:32,279
What other evidence is there

210
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:35,159
to charge Chu Yunchang
as the Jade Squirrel?

211
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,759
My Lord, I recently engaged
the Jade Squirrel in a duel.

212
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,679
She was suffering from an old injury,

213
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,399
which flared up during our fight.

214
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:45,679
Chu Yunchang's injury flared up
at that same time.

215
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,840
This is ironclad proof.

216
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,159
Vice Minister,

217
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,320
Yunchang's injury

218
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,350
was sustained from Li Wan
while saving my sister.

219
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,799
She is a fragile young woman.

220
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,280
After suffering a severe wound,

221
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,440
it's only natural

222
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:56,679
for it to flare up.

223
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,279
Summon Mao Wenrong.

224
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,600
Yes, sir.

225
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,480
Summon Mao Wenrong!

226
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:07,960
Vice Minister,

227
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,080
Chu Yunchang's injuries

228
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,960
were indeed sustained while saving me.

229
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:13,559
On the night at Prince Duan's Residence,

230
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:15,159
I was in Chu Yunchang's room
the entire time

231
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:15,960
watching over her.

232
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:18,159
I never personally saw her leave.

233
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:20,879
Rong!

234
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,399
Wushuang,

235
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,879
I am simply telling the truth,

236
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:24,840
without bias.

237
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,919
Even if I disliked Chu Yunchang
a hundred times over,

238
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,879
I would never frame her.

239
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:34,440
Hear the verdict.

240
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,200
The prisoner Lin Xin'er has
taken her own life.

241
00:10:38,412 --> 00:10:39,971
Identify the body and close the case.

242
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,520
There is insufficient evidence
to convict Chu Yunchang.

243
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,519
She is released.

244
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,240
Luo Wushuang,

245
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:54,399
you dared to detain
a civilian without proof

246
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:56,840
and turned this case
into an absolute mess.

247
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:59,000
You are a reckless fool.

248
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,480
Report to the Personnel Corps.

249
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,360
You are demoted.

250
00:11:03,062 --> 00:11:03,799
Vice Minister...

251
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,080
Hear me out.

252
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,440
Silence!

253
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:12,240
The Jade Squirrel has been
terrorizing the Capital for days,

254
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:15,240
robbing countess noble households.

255
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,120
You can't catch the real thief,

256
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,879
so you try to scapegoat a young girl?

257
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,360
Unbelievable!

258
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:24,399
I order you to catch
the real Jade Squirrel

259
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:26,559
within a hundred days.

260
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,639
If you try to fool me

261
00:11:28,639 --> 00:11:30,000
with another fake...

262
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,639
Commissioner Luo,

263
00:11:37,879 --> 00:11:40,080
you shall share the blame as well.

264
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:41,840
Understood.

265
00:11:44,770 --> 00:11:45,559
Vice Minister Zhou!

266
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,200
Wuzhuang!

267
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,200
Chang.

268
00:11:59,879 --> 00:12:00,799
Is your hand okay?

269
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:05,480
What is it?

270
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,320
Still feeling slighted?

271
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,840
It's my own fault for failing
to find concrete proof.

272
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,960
I'm the reason
Chu Yunchang walked away.

273
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,080
Here.

274
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,080
Have a taste.

275
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,480
I've called you impulsive.

276
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,480
You still haven't changed.

277
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,720
No wonder you were outsmarted again.

278
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:34,639
Grandpa...

279
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,679
Do you find Chu Yunchang

280
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:37,500
suspicious as well?

281
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,080
You have such a low tolerance
for this woman.

282
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,840
Is it because you truly doubt her,

283
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,679
or because of Mao Buyu?

284
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:49,480
It's both.

285
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,720
Professionally,

286
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,360
even if she isn't the Jade Squirrel,

287
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,960
she's definitely
with the Sacred Hand Sect.

288
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,720
She's a sworn enemy of our Gate Bureau.

289
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,919
And personally,

290
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:58,840
Grandpa, you know where I stand.

291
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:01,679
If I didn't have feelings for Mao Buyu,

292
00:13:01,919 --> 00:13:03,960
I never would have agreed
to the blind date.

293
00:13:04,759 --> 00:13:07,039
Buyu and I are of equal status.

294
00:13:07,039 --> 00:13:07,960
A perfect match.

295
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,840
So I won't let some suspicious outsider

296
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,679
come and play him for a fool.

297
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,279
So, for duty and for love,

298
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:19,840
you refuse to let that Chu girl go.

299
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:20,960
Yes.

300
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,480
Good.

301
00:13:23,279 --> 00:13:25,320
Then, you must be even more cautious.

302
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,720
If you truly believe Chu Yunchang

303
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,200
is the Jade Squirrel,

304
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:30,320
then you're dealing with

305
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:33,559
the world's newly-crowned Grandmaster.

306
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,120
Do you really think

307
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,360
she would let you catch her so easily?

308
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,320
I got too impatient this time.

309
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,480
It's just like the tea in your hand.

310
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:43,360
You won't know if it's truly

311
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,440
a good blend

312
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,639
until you've reached the very bottom.

313
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:56,879
Chang, what's the matter?

314
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:57,960
It's nothing.

315
00:13:58,879 --> 00:13:59,480
Chang...

316
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:04,000
You definitely don't look "fine."

317
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:09,600
I had no idea Luo Wushuang
was so obsessed with you.

318
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:16,200
Is that what's bothering you?

319
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,879
That's not like you at all.

320
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:19,600
You're the only one who gets me.

321
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,360
Of course I do.

322
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,559
No matter what anyone says,

323
00:14:25,559 --> 00:14:27,279
I will always believe in you.

324
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:28,639
It's not that I'm naive

325
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:29,720
or lack better judgment.

326
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:30,879
It's just...

327
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,840
I know my Chang

328
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:35,360
could never be a wicked villain.

329
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:37,960
So no matter what your reasons are,

330
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,960
you can tell me.

331
00:14:41,537 --> 00:14:42,712
(Yunchang Flower Shop)

332
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,000
Does it hurt?

333
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:49,679
No.

334
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:50,480
It's just a scratch.

335
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,440
I'll say it one last time.

336
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:56,840
Even if you're protecting
the Jade Squirrel

337
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:58,519
because you're indebted to her,

338
00:14:58,759 --> 00:14:59,679
I don't care.

339
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,519
We'll face the past together,

340
00:15:02,519 --> 00:15:03,600
and we'll handle

341
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:05,559
whatever the future holds.

342
00:15:06,399 --> 00:15:07,000
But...

343
00:15:08,039 --> 00:15:09,399
you have to promise me one thing.

344
00:15:15,912 --> 00:15:19,187
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

345
00:15:19,225 --> 00:15:22,100
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

346
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:28,318
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

347
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:32,820
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

348
00:15:32,950 --> 00:15:35,870
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

349
00:15:37,038 --> 00:15:42,278
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

350
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:45,893
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

351
00:15:45,893 --> 00:15:49,543
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

352
00:15:49,612 --> 00:15:53,102
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

353
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:56,175
♪To the ends of time♪

354
00:15:56,175 --> 00:15:59,550
♪The moon traces your face♪

355
00:15:59,737 --> 00:16:03,325
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

356
00:16:03,325 --> 00:16:09,565
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

357
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:13,115
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

358
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:16,938
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

359
00:16:17,225 --> 00:16:20,250
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

360
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:23,350
♪On our way to forever♪

361
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:27,200
♪The moon traces your face♪

362
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:30,560
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

363
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:36,710
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

364
00:16:37,787 --> 00:16:47,427
♪Just to be with you♪

